result.name: Yuen Long Hop Lun Noodles

reviews.text: Tasty assorted pork - literally all parts of a Pig in soup. Traditional Cantonese and Chou Chow flavor. 😜
It offers different types of soup noodles and pic inners, fresh, tasty and interesting (for me). Too bad no English menu.
Very authentic and homely taste, no trace of MSG!
Tasty fishball noodles in white pepper pork booth. Appetitizer icy cold squid is an interesting fusion dish that eats like sashimi.

Like their food, but the environment is not that great, at least the seatings are bad.
Here served Chinese noodle, and just like cart noodle, you can select your side dishes as listed, you have to select your order from the menu paper, and submit it to the staffs.
Food here is good, especially the soup of the noodle.  However the seatings are packed, the staff required you to sit into a small table with 6 customers.  And as other noodle shop, they expect you to leave asap once you finished.
I do not recommend a group of people come here, as there are too many people, so you probably need to sit on different tables, as here is not a good place for chit chat too

result.name: 元朗合隆潮州粉麵

reviews.text: 光顧了2次了，是值得一試餐廳，店舖在橫街，有遠離煩囂感覺， 點細豬雜便可嚐多個豬的部份。而麵身有多個選擇，可惜我較喜歡傳統的油麵，這裡麵身較軟；但有銀針粉可選擇，相信一般麵店比較少有。
價錢合理，份量也足，湯頭鲜，醉鷄入味，邪惡的豬油撈飯一定要試
價錢公道，冰鎮墨魚最好食，花雕雞亦好好味。

主打係豬什粉麵，另有其他特色小食。

豬什味道不錯，無乜"騷味"

地方整潔，招呼還可。

食物質素：⭐⭐⭐⭐
食物價格：⭐⭐⭐
服務質素：⭐⭐⭐
環境舒適：⭐⭐⭐
整體而言：⭐⭐⭐⭐
這裏的裝修很有舊香港的感覺，很有特色。 地方很乾淨，枱與枱之間的空間也很足夠，冷氣也很充足。 食物方面，豬雜湯的湯底很鮮甜，豬雜爽口沒有腥味，很好吃。
